This script calculates the distance between two locations using the Haversine formula. It accepts latitude and longitude inputs, handles errors, and outputs the result in kilometers or miles.

---

## ✅ Features:
- Accepts latitude and longitude inputs for two locations.
- Calculates distance using the Haversine formula.
